17. @benefitcosmetics the porefessional super setter spray

text:
✔️Pacifica Sunny Glow vs Drunk Elephant Di Bronzi Drops

These Pacifica drops are like a liquid bronzer you can mix with your moisturizer, under makeup, as a bronzer or however you want. Heads up for sensitive skin: it does have added fragrance. It’s not very noticeable when applying but something to watch out for if you’re prone to irritation

✔️Neutrogena Healthy Glow Perfector Pen vs YSL touché éclat

Neutrogena is the best concealer brand. The radiant creamy concealer is my favorite for everyday and this brightener is a new fave for a no makeup look. It’s a cross between ysl touché éclat and the rare beauty brightener. Very hydrating with light to medium coverage.

✔️Elf Reviver Lip Oil vs Dior Lip Oil

The elf lip oil is really comfortable and thin in consistency. Don’t be intimidated by the color in the tube because it goes on quite sheer. This and the nyx lip oil are the two closest to Dior that I’ve tried.

My weekly deep clean routine! I never reuse dirty brushes on clients because proper sanitation puts my mind at ease.
•
-Dawn Dish Soap Antibacterial (used to clean handles and some of the bristles
-@ShopMissA brush cleaner (my favorite soap!) and Lelevani UV Sterilizer machine (sanitized with UV and dries the brushes completely within 2.5 hours)
-@Benefit Cosmetics Get Unlocked Oil Cleanser (used as a first step when cleaning brushes that have liquid foundation or concealer)
@Cinema Secrets Pro Cosmetics Brush Cleaner (you can use it before deep cleaning, but I like to follow up as a last step with my foundation and concealer brushes to get out any trapped dirt or product)
